M|marcus||---------|-------|--------------|
M|marcus|| **Novizio** | Premium fashion brand (B2C, soc-led) | Brand awareness and cnt growth |
M|marcus|| **Hourbour** | Financial app (SaaS, subscription) | MRR growth and user retention |
